OL,3,CBirmingham City Council considering
OL,4,C20mph speed limits across city
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council will today
OL,7,Fdiscuss plans to make the city's roads
OL,8,Fsafer, including introducing 20mph
OL,9,Fspeed limits across large parts of the
OL,10,Fcity.
OL,12,FIn July of this year, the council
OL,13,Fdeclared a road safety emergency and
OL,14,Fplans to reduce the 40mph speed limit
OL,15,Fto 30mph.
OL,17,FSoon after, an inquiry began into
OL,18,Ftraffic-related problems in the city,
OL,19,Fincluding road safety, but also
OL,20,Fcovering illegal parking.
