OL,3,CBirmingham City Council considering
OL,4,C20mph speed limits across city
OL,6,FThe report identified that reducing
OL,7,Fspeed limits would also reduce "the
OL,8,Fnumbers of people killed or seriously
OL,9,Finjured on roads."
OL,11,FThe Cabinet Member for Environment and
OL,12,FTransport, Councillor Majid Mahmood,
OL,13,Fhas sent a letter to Government
OL,14,Frequesting a 20mph zone for the whole
OL,15,Fof Birmingham.
OL,17,FIn a statement, Mr Mahmood said that
OL,18,Fslower speed limits on appropriate
OL,19,Froads would reduce collisions and save
OL,20,Flives.
