OL,3,CBirmingham City Council considering
OL,4,C20mph speed limits across city
OL,6,F"For this reason, our Birmingham
OL,7,FTransport Plan sets out that 20mph
OL,8,Fshould be the speed limit in
OL,9,Fresidential areas and where footfall
OL,10,Fis high," he said.
OL,12,F"Other types of roads will remain
OL,13,Funaffected. Additionally, slower
OL,14,Fspeeds are less intimidating towards
OL,15,Fthose who walk or cycle - activities
OL,16,Fthat we need to encourage more of if
OL,17,Fwe are to reduce the number of harmful
OL,18,Femissions and traffic levels in the
OL,19,Fcity."
