OL,3,CBirmingham City Council considering
OL,4,C20mph speed limits across city
OL,6,FHe continued: "Approximately one third
OL,7,Fof the city's roads are already
OL,8,Fsubject to a 20mph speed limit. We
OL,9,Fwould like to expand the number of
OL,10,Froads subject to this speed limit
OL,11,Fwhere appropriate and are currently
OL,12,Fexploring opportunities to carry this
OL,13,Fout."
OL,15,FCllr Mahmood added in the report that
OL,16,Fa '20mph zone' in Wales had
OL,17,Fhighlighted there would be "cost
OL,18,Fimplications" for Birmingham council
OL,19,Fin implementing something similar.
