OL,3,CBirmingham City Council considering
OL,4,C20mph speed limits across city
OL,6,FPlans to introduce more 20mph limits
OL,7,Fin Birmingham must go through a
OL,8,Fconsultation first.
OL,10,FCouncillor David Barker, who chaired
OL,11,Fthe inquiry into road safety, says:
OL,12,F"Now is the time to follow words with
OL,13,Factions and demonstrate to the
OL,14,Fresidents of Birmingham how this
OL,15,Fcouncil will make changes to deliver
OL,16,Fsafer streets and roads for all of us."
